---
import { ScrollReveal } from '~/components/ui/cyber';
---

<section class="scroll-mt-16 bg-white dark:bg-cyber-black transition-colors duration-300" id="vision">
	<div class="px-4 py-16 mx-auto max-w-6xl lg:px-8 lg:py-20">
		<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
			<ScrollReveal client:visible variant="slide-up">
				<div class="text-center mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-6 font-display text-black dark:text-white uppercase">
						未来科技<span class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-neon-blue">创新空间</span>
					</h2>
					<p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-medium">
						猫头鹰实验室致力于为每一位探索者打造充满惊喜的创新之旅，培养面向未来的创新人才
					</p>
				</div>
			</ScrollReveal>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
				<!-- Card 1 -->
				<ScrollReveal client:visible variant="brutal" delay={0}>
					<div class="h-full bg-white dark:bg-black/40 p-6 border-4 border-black dark:border-amber-500/50 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] dark:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(245,158,11,0.2)] hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[12px_12px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] dark:hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(245,158,11,0.4)] transition-all duration-200 group">
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 mb-6 border-4 border-black dark:border-amber-500 bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/20 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-200">
							<span class="font-display font-black text-4xl text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400">!</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 text-black dark:text-white font-display uppercase">激发想象</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-medium leading-relaxed">
							每个孩子都是天生的创造者。在这里，天马行空的想法不仅被接纳，更被鼓励、培育和实现。
						</p>
					</div>
				</ScrollReveal>

				<!-- Card 2 -->
				<ScrollReveal client:visible variant="brutal" delay={0.1}>
					<div class="h-full bg-white dark:bg-black/40 p-6 border-4 border-black dark:border-rose-500/50 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] dark:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(244,63,94,0.2)] hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[12px_12px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] dark:hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(244,63,94,0.4)] transition-all duration-200 group">
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 mb-6 border-4 border-black dark:border-rose-500 bg-rose-100 dark:bg-rose-900/20 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-200">
							<span class="font-display font-black text-4xl text-rose-600 dark:text-rose-400">♥</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 text-black dark:text-white font-display uppercase">创造快乐</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-medium leading-relaxed">
							学习应该是充满乐趣的探险。我们让探索过程本身成为最大的奖励，让创新成为最好的体验。
						</p>
					</div>
				</ScrollReveal>

				<!-- Card 3 -->
				<ScrollReveal client:visible variant="brutal" delay={0.2}>
					<div class="h-full bg-white dark:bg-black/40 p-6 border-4 border-black dark:border-emerald-500/50 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] dark:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(16,185,129,0.2)] hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[12px_12px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] dark:hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(16,185,129,0.4)] transition-all duration-200 group">
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 mb-6 border-4 border-black dark:border-emerald-500 bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-900/20 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-200">
							<span class="font-display font-black text-4xl text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">∞</span>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 text-black dark:text-white font-display uppercase">面向未来</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-medium leading-relaxed">
							培养AI时代不可替代的能力：批判性思维、创造力、协作能力和情感智慧。
						</p>
					</div>
				</ScrollReveal>
			</div>

			<!-- Quote Section -->
			<ScrollReveal client:visible variant="slide-up" delay={0.3}>
				<div class="bg-indigo-600 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 border-4 border-black dark:border-indigo-500 p-8 text-white shadow-[12px_12px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] dark:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(79,70,229,0.3)] relative overflow-hidden">
					<!-- Background Grid -->
					<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.2)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.2)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:20px_20px]"></div>

					<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center md:items-start">
						<div class="flex-shrink-0">
							<div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white text-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center border-4 border-black font-serif text-6xl font-bold">
								"
							</div>
						</div>
						<div>
							<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-6 leading-relaxed font-display tracking-tight">
								想象力比知识更重要，因为知识是有限的，而想象力概括着世界上的一切，推动着进步，并且是知识进化的源泉。
							</p>
							<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
								<div class="h-1 w-12 bg-white"></div>
								<p class="text-lg font-mono font-bold uppercase">阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦</p>
							</div>
							<div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-black/20 border-2 border-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm">
								<p class="text-base font-mono leading-relaxed">
									> 猫头鹰实验室是一个不断进化的创新生态。<br>
									> 我们相信，只要好奇心还在，探索就永不止步。
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</ScrollReveal>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
